{"tid":2115204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張竹君：武肺大爆發下的 4 個生存提示","createTime":"2020-07-19T10:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T19:36:03.000Z","uid":7542,"like":477,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"349f6a30894c1158ce12ce6df18e676a99dda2fa","tid":2115204,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>唔該香港人醒醒定定！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(1) <strong>市民接觸錢幣後，切勿接觸眼、口、鼻及盡早洗手</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(2) <strong>個別個案只曾與確診者短時間接觸，可能沒有戴口罩時間只數分鐘都有染疫</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(3)<strong>不少個案涉外出用膳及打麻雀，她呼籲市民減少社交活動</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(4) <strong>希望年長及長期病患者，能盡量留家切勿外出。如果家中有高危病人，同住者外出也有機會帶病毒返家，也應盡量避免外出 </strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: 記者會 live"},{"pid":"535ded40156387ddde71e24f0ec3d062f196795c","tid":2115204,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87e4bdd4eae205aec1f64c2677f4a6f00522408","tid":2115204,"uid":89517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55491a31411666b6718a2bcf8f4774d96247c72f","tid":2115204,"uid":151534,"like":108,"dislike":2,"score":106,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:49:27.000Z","msg":"明天照常上班<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog